{"tid":2231890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辦聯署呼籲德國制裁中國　聯署成功會有聽證會　被建制派瘋狂狙擊","createTime":"2020-10-06T04:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T00:24:37.000Z","uid":261647,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"20f30896b84e7b2ea44b1879c07d6136b6c67901","tid":2231890,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201003/s00002/1601661294333/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201003%2Fs00002%2F1601661294333%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=84fc1c8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201003%2Fs00002%2F1601661294333%2F&h=0a4cff7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20201003/s00002/1601661294333/</a><br />\n<br />\n被網民稱為「滑鼠娘娘」嘅鄺頌晴（圖）𠵱家喺德國讀書，佢早排喺當地發起聯署，呼籲德國聯邦議會制裁侵害人權嘅中國官員，以及促請德國政府向香港發出旅遊警示等。佢呢個行徑惹嚟建制派及親中傳媒狙擊。《文匯報》噚日報道就搵嚟人大代表陳曼琪等人，話鄺頌晴有可能違反《港區國安法》第29條第4款，即係對中央及特區政府進行制裁、封鎖等敵對行為，又話要追究。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/ED3UIWAA7VAS7NSQEMTD3D5RNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FED3UIWAA7VAS7NSQEMTD3D5RNM%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=6dfc04b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FED3UIWAA7VAS7NSQEMTD3D5RNM%2F&h=044ead7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/ED3UIWAA7VAS7NSQEMTD3D5RNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有五萬人參與聯署，德國國會就會舉行有關制裁中國嘅聽證會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/10/glacier-kwong-being-threatened-by-so-called-civil-servant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fglacier-kwong-being-threatened-by-so-called-civil-servant%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=f607c865\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/10/glacier-kwong-being-threatened-by-so-called-civil-servant/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/glacier-kwong-being-threatened-732x530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fglacier-kwong-being-threatened-732x530.jpg&h=4449032a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3c4638b583ae0bc9ee334840e17b92590d1d4e5","tid":2231890,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2873b1583c16878af04e549d0a3ea893f7b6b96f","tid":2231890,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a25e32219091bbfd8c7f7b071bf7a7ae20f9a82","tid":2231890,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"公狗仲想做公務員?以香港人身份叫你，共狗你好收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7936f5320846a8ec19891d24249bc0b70b605597","tid":2231890,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11982ea0384b0d3ca5a454d110ceb9034f3eade4","tid":2231890,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"oh"},{"pid":"f958de81934e16deb37e23f54a0d7948a2fcb3ae","tid":2231890,"uid":224755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"證明呢個聯署有用"},{"pid":"34207dd4f186f37